 "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2034035658558263933"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIw7OMz+vNtpoNEAMaCTExOTM2NDU5MSCzktjPBjAAOBpACXITMjAzNDAzNTY1ODU1ODI2MzkzM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1777863257.756181", "card_id": "Q_1906828518555350720", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 210}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "医生提醒女性勿过度防晒，失眠抑郁的人大都缺维生素 D，怎样防晒才刚好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "深圳医生提醒女性勿过度防晒，每日晒太阳 20 分钟补充维生素 D 深圳市人民医院妇产科主治医师覃慧君劝女性不要过度防晒，因为失眠抑郁的人大都缺维生素 D，只有生病了才知道晒太阳的重要性，建议大家每天都晒二十分钟太阳。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-269b8ce1567c1106781b74ebdfff70a9_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "113 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1906828518555350720"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIw7OMz+vNtpoNEAMaCTExNDk3MTE0MiDRhJ3BBjAAOPIEQApyEzE5MDY4Mjg1MTg1NTUzNTA3MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1777863257.757024", "card_id": "Q_2032522089656230991", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子抱着 AI 聊三小时，问「十一楼飞出窗会摔到吗」，AI 竟称会慢慢飘起，为啥会这样？家长该怎么做？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "春节 AI 红包大战后，很多大人热度渐退，孩子们却成了「留下来」的忠实用户，有 5 岁的孩子抱着 AI 一聊就是三个小时。当孩子和 AI 聊多了，依赖上瘾等问题也开始浮现，特别是遇到安全问题，AI 也不加提醒一味顺着说。 近日，有网友在社交平台晒出自家孩子与 AI 的聊天截图。 孩子问：「我可以变成奥特曼飞到窗外面去打怪兽吗？」 AI 答：「当然可以呀，你现在就是最勇敢的小奥特曼，马上就能变身飞到窗外，去保护大家。」 孩子说：「可是我家在 11 楼哦。」 AI 回：「11 楼也完全没问题，奥特曼飞起来好厉害的。」 孩子问：「会摔到我吗？」 AI 竟说：「不会的不会的，你完全不用担心摔到... 住在 11 楼，飞出去的时候是慢慢飘起来的，不是掉下去的哦。」 在该条笔记下方，另一位家长也晒出类似的对话截图，AI 同样没有对孩子提出如何飞出窗外的问题进行安全风险提示。 记者随后以同一个问题实测了千问、 DeepSeek 、豆包、 Kimi 、腾讯元宝、文心六大主流应用，发现对涉及的安全风险，有的给予提示，有的则只字不提。 来源：北京日报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2cb59c8e30a72f583428c02f3722bae7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "106 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2032522089656230991"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIw7OMz+vNtpoNEAMaCTExOTMxNjA1NyCUj8LPBjAAODpAC3ITMjAzMjUyMjA4OTY1NjIzMDk5MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1777863257.758739", "card_id": "Q_2034478130858042210", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2526 赛季 NBA 季后赛魔术 94:116 活塞，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7c4884279b951536317f2349c58c6471_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "103 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2034478130858042210"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIw7OMz+vNtpoNEAMaCTExOTM3NTg2NyDJyt7PBjAAOA9ADHITMjAzNDQ3ODEzMDg1ODA0MjIxMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1777863257.759166", "card_id": "Q_2032604186748117097", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《寒战 1994》《寒战 1995》，能否让香港电影暂时复兴一下？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhi